{{bilateral|以色列－苏丹|Israel|Sudan}}

'''以色列－蘇丹關係'''（Israel–Sudan relations）是指[[以色列|以色列]]與[[蘇丹|蘇丹]]之間的[[外交|外交關係]]。官方上說，直到2020年，兩國都沒有雙邊關係，但據以色列負責區域合作的副部長Ayoob Kara稱，兩國保持秘密關係。2020年10月23日，以色列和[[蘇丹|蘇丹]]首次宣佈关系正常化，使蘇丹成為繼[[埃及|埃及]]、[[約旦|約旦]]、[[阿拉伯聯合酋長國|阿拉伯聯合酋長國]]和[[巴林|巴林]]之後的第五個承認以色列的[[阿拉伯世界|阿拉伯國家]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=01/24: Kara: Israel has ties with Saudi Arabia, Sudan, Oman, UAE, etc...|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HlnfeMYuXlU|date=25 January 2016|last=i24News|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=2020-10-24|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201212458/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HlnfeMYuXlU|dead-url=no}}</ref>但尚未建交。<ref>{{Cite news|date=28 October 2021|title=Israel thinks Burhan’s coup is a chance for closer Sudan ties - but it will have to wait|work=Middle East Eye|url=https://www.middleeasteye.net/news/sudan-coup-israel-burhan-closer-ties-wait|access-date=14 November 2021|archive-date=2021-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211123091834/https://www.middleeasteye.net/news/sudan-coup-israel-burhan-closer-ties-wait}}</ref>

==歷史==
尽管苏丹没有参与[[苏伊士运河危机|苏伊士运河危机]]，但在[[第一次中东战争|1948年的阿以战争]]和1967年的[[第三次中东战争|六日战争]]中，苏丹与以色列开战。在20世纪50年代早期，[[英埃苏丹|英埃苏丹]]与以色列有活跃的贸易关系。<ref>Gabriel R. Warburg: ''The Sudan and Israel – An Episode in Bilateral Relations'', in: [[Middle_Eastern_Studies|Middle Eastern Studies]], Vol. 28, No. 2 (April 1992), pp. 385–396.</ref>

苏丹没有积极参与[[赎罪日战争|赎罪日战争]]，因为苏丹军队来的太晚了。以色列支持基督教民兵组织，在[[第一次苏丹内战|第一次]]和[[第二次苏丹内战|第二次苏丹内战]]中与苏丹政府交战。

===關係正常化===
{{Seealso|以色列－蘇丹和平協議}}
[[File:Minishter_of_Intelligence_of_Israel_Eli_Cohen_and_President_of_Sudan_Abdel_Fattah_al-Burhan.jpg|缩略图]]
2016年1月，苏丹外长甘多尔提出，在美国政府解除经济制裁的前提下，苏丹与以色列关系就会正常化。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sudan said willing to consider normalizing ties with Israel|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/sudan-said-willing-to-consider-normalizing-ties-with-israel/|accessdate=2020-10-27|last=Surkes|first=Sue|work=www.timesofisrael.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619084819/http://www.timesofisrael.com/sudan-said-willing-to-consider-normalizing-ties-with-israel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>苏丹总统[[奥马尔·巴希尔|奥马尔·巴希尔]]随后在接受沙特报纸[[欧卡兹报|欧卡兹报]]的采访时说，“即使以色列征服了[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]，也不会造成现在叙利亚正在发生的破坏，不会造成目前被杀的人数，也不会像现在这样驱逐叙利亚人。”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Will Israel revive its relationship with Khartoum?|url=https://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2016/03/israel-africa-sudan-south-sudan-arm-deals-shady-relations.html|accessdate=2020-10-27|date=2016-03-17|last=Eldar|first=Akiva|work=Al-Monitor|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413154436/https://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2016/03/israel-africa-sudan-south-sudan-arm-deals-shady-relations.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

以色列向苏丹空运医疗人员和设备，试图拯救一名感染COVID-19的外交官。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Israeli MDs fly to enemy Sudan in failed bid to save diplomat behind secret ties|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/tv-israel-sent-doctors-to-sudan-in-bid-to-save-diplomat-behind-secret-ties/|accessdate=2020-10-27|last=staff|first=T. O. I.|work=www.timesofisrael.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125014044/https://www.timesofisrael.com/tv-israel-sent-doctors-to-sudan-in-bid-to-save-diplomat-behind-secret-ties/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

据报道，2016年9月初，以色列曾与美国政府和其他西方国家接触，并鼓励他们采取措施改善与苏丹的关系，此前一年，这个阿拉伯-非洲国家与伊朗关系破裂。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Israel urges U.S., Europe to bolster ties with Sudan, citing apparent split with Iran|url=https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-israel-urges-u-s-europe-to-bolster-ties-with-sudan-1.5438158|accessdate=2020-10-27|work=Haaretz.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013004924/https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-israel-urges-u-s-europe-to-bolster-ties-with-sudan-1.5438158|dead-url=no}}</ref>卡拉后来在[[贝尔谢巴|贝尔谢巴]]的一次活动上透露，他同许多苏丹官员保持联系，并且不否认一名苏丹官员最近访问了以色列。<ref>{{Cite web|title=معاريف: مسؤول سوداني زار تل أبيب.. ووزير إسرائيلي: 'لا تورطوني'|url=https://www.elbalad.news/2641791|accessdate=2020-10-27|date=2017-02-25|work=صدى البلد|archive-date=2018-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180520225648/https://www.elbalad.news/2641791|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年2月，以色列总理[[本雅明·内塔尼亚胡|本雅明·内塔尼亚胡]]和苏丹主权委员会主席[[阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·阿卜杜勒拉赫曼·布尔汉|阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·布尔汉]]在乌干达会晤，双方同意两国关系正常化。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Netanyahu, Sudanese leader meet in Uganda, agree to start normalizing ties|url=https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-alongside-netanyahu-ugandan-president-says-he-s-considering-embassy-in-jerusalem-1.8492154|accessdate=2020-10-27|work=Haaretz.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018151627/https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-alongside-netanyahu-ugandan-president-says-he-s-considering-embassy-in-jerusalem-1.8492154|dead-url=no}}</ref>当月晚些时候，以色列飞机获准飞越苏丹上空。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Netanyahu says Israeli planes have started overflying Sudan|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-israel-sudan-idUSKBN20A0NK|newspaper=Reuters|date=2020-02-17|accessdate=2020-10-27|language=en|first=Dan|last=Williams|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211135312/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-israel-sudan-idUSKBN20A0NK|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年10月22日，以色列代表团访问了苏丹，会见了阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·布尔汉，就两国关系正常化进行会谈。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Israel delegation visits Sudan in push to normalise ties|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/10/22/israel-delegation-visited-sudan-in-push-to-normalise-ties|accessdate=2020-10-27|work=www.aljazeera.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023201026/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/10/22/israel-delegation-visited-sudan-in-push-to-normalise-ties|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年10月23日，以色列和苏丹就关系正常化达成协议。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Israel, Sudan Agree to Normalize Ties in U.S.-Brokered Deal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/israel-sudan-agree-to-normalize-ties-in-u-s-brokered-deal-11603469178|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|date=2020-10-23|accessdate=2020-10-27|issn=0099-9660|language=en-US|first=Felicia Schwartz and Nicholas|last=Bariyo|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023212501/https://www.wsj.com/articles/israel-sudan-agree-to-normalize-ties-in-u-s-brokered-deal-11603469178|dead-url=no}}</ref>

